condition.p:
The manuscript contains a large number of erasures, possibly by the scribe,
                        possibly by a later hand, but in any case for the most part not filled in;
                        for example on fol. 3ra, lines 15-16 there are two erasures,
                        the first of perhaps 16, the second of six characters, and four lines of text
                        have been erased on fol. 5vb following line 21.
